ch.epfl.lis.wingj.expression

Class ExpressionMapsAggregator

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.epfl.lis.wingj.expression.ExpressionMapsAggregator

  • public class ExpressionMapsAggregator
extends java.lang.Object
    Aggregates many expression maps together to get a unique model.

    UPDATE: Now supports the use of different structures for generating the target aggregated structure.

    Version:
    November 28, 2011
    Author:
    Thomas Schaffter (thomas.schaff...@gmail.com), Ricard Delgado-Gonzalo (ricard.delg...@gmail.com)
